\b \cf0 Statically-configured table views
\b0 \
\
A table view can be configured, using the storyboard, with statically-configured items. \
This enables you to use it as a "launch" menu.\
\
This app's (root) table view shows two groups. The top group enables drill-down navigation. \
\
The app's model object has a general-purpose "fetch" method. It returns an array of fetch results.\
Each row in the table view's top group configures and executes a fetch request. \
The results are passed on to the next-level controller.\
\

